Jordan/Zalaznick Capital Co., an affiliate of Jordan Co., a New York investment firm, and Mezzanine Capital & Income Trust PLC, have acquired all shares outstanding of Custom Chrome Inc.
The price wasn't disclosed. 

Ty Cruze, Custom Chrome's founder and chief executive officer, and other senior managers also have a stake in the company and will continue in their current roles. 

Custom Chrome, based in Morgan Hill, Calif., supplies motorcycle parts and accessories to the Harley-Davidson aftermarket.
Mezzanine Capital is a British investment trust company.
Jordan said it has investments in more than 40 companies throughout the U.S. 

